# Capital OS - Backend API

## Environment Variables
```
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://postgres:password@localhost:5432/capitalos
SECRET_KEY=your-super-secret-key-change-in-production
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
TRUELAYER_CLIENT_ID=your-truelayer-client-id
TRUELAYER_CLIENT_SECRET=your-truelayer-client-secret
TRUELAYER_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8000/banks/callback
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173
```